  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9c\u0dc4 \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who stole goods from Temple Tree was caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Western Province South Crime Division says that a person who entered the Araliya Gaha Mandir under the guise of activists and stole its property was arrested in Rajagiriya Bandaranaike.",
        "More than 200 years old brass wall decorations, camera equipment and a camera bag were found in the suspect's house.",
        "The police say that the suspect entered the Araliyagaha Mandir with another group and stole wall decorations from the media unit.",
        "Investigations are being conducted to arrest a group of other suspects"
      ],
